{"tid":956120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高級助理警務處處長李志恒日本小樽遇車禍　無生命危險","createTime":"2018-12-26T04:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T05:28:53.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a8ca2d1c55fd86dd06dd74a7973839e22b9f510","tid":956120,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T04:32:37.000Z","msg":"高級助理警務處處長李志恒在日本小樽旅行期間遇車禍，他與同行6人被送往3間不同醫院。<br />\n<br />\n事發後，李志恒清醒但下身痳痺，無生命危險，透過入境處1868熱線轉介協助，由直升機轉往另一醫院。<br />\n<br />\n事發在昨日，當時有兩輛車迎頭相撞，李志恒頸部受傷，已接受手術，同車其餘人士輕傷。警隊福利部及入境處派員到當地協助，李志恒自行致電回港向上司講述事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1435059-20181226.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1435059-20181226.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=nlZSAbnHmEPvOkfLRhKZ1G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9e161484\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1435059-20181226.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=aa13882a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1435059-20181226.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c8f59a5434064bcf58eaaa4e466c11d6a4807b10","tid":956120,"uid":17496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T05:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11b3cb4ffa85e22d168534ea94d56bf1440ca503","tid":956120,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T05:10:35.000Z","msg":"可惜可惜"},{"pid":"111baaa482cb9e6fe82821caf298aac937ec564f","tid":956120,"uid":146631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T05:28:53.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"}]}